---
const { whatsappLink } = Astro.props;
---
<section id="harga" class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-14">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Paket Layanan</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Pilih paket yang paling sesuai untuk membantu proyek IoT dan skripsi Anda selesai dengan lancar.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="mb-5">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Paket Software</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Untuk mahasiswa yang sudah memiliki hardware dan butuh perangkat lunak lengkap.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Harga mulai</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold">Diskon 25%</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 line-through mb-2">Rp 1.000.000</p>
                    <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Rp 750.000</p>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600 mb-8">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="mt-1 text-orange-500">•</span>
                        <span>Source code program dan dashboard UI</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="mt-1 text-orange-500">•</span>
                        <span>Konsultasi online sampai selesai</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="mt-1 text-orange-500">•</span>
                        <span>Revisi program sampai sesuai</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href={whatsappLink} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full rounded-full bg-orange-500 px-6 py-3 text-white font-semibold transition hover:bg-orange-600">Tanya Paket</a>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-[2rem] border-2 border-orange-500 bg-white p-8 shadow-xl">
                <div class="mb-5">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-orange-500 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-bold text-white mb-4">Paling Laris</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Paket Full Package</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Solusi lengkap dengan perangkat siap pakai dan dukungan penuh dari tim kami.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Harga mulai</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold">Diskon 25%</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 line-through mb-2">Rp 2.000.000</p>
                    <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Rp 1.500.000</p>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600 mb-8">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="mt-1 text-orange-500">•</span>
                        <span>Software + hardware siap pakai</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="mt-1 text-orange-500">•</span>
                        <span>Perakitan dan pengujian alat</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="mt-1 text-orange-500">•</span>
                        <span>Support pasca pengiriman</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href={whatsappLink} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full rounded-full bg-orange-500 px-6 py-3 text-white font-semibold transition hover:bg-orange-600">Tanya Paket</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
